name: Learningalgorithms
tagline: A good place to learn and implement famous algorithms
body:
### Welcome to Learning Algorithms.
This repository is created for coding examples on implementation of good and world famous algorithms.

Here you can learn the algorithms as well as contribute for others to learn.

### Authors and Contributors
Current Contributors: Ankur Srivastava (@ankcrimson), Waiting for others to join this list.

### Support or Contact
